    <main class="main">
        <section>
            <h2>Overview</h2>
            <p>Hire-Purchase Credit allows buyers to acquire property through structured periodic payments while gaining immediate use of the asset. FSTL ensures credit agreements are secure, legally verified, and enforceable.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Why Hire-Purchase Credit Matters in Nigeria</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Facilitates home ownership for low and middle-income families</li>
                <li>Addresses the Nigeria housing deficit, currently over 17 million units</li>
                <li>Encourages banks and financial institutions to participate in long-term lending</li>
                <li>Supports the growth of a robust mortgage and property finance culture</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>FSTL Methodology</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>Due diligence on property and borrower documentation</li>
                <li>Structured repayment schedules to match borrower capacity</li>
                <li>Integration with Title Guarantee and Mortgage Insurance</li>
                <li>Blockchain-based verification for transparency and trust</li>
            </ol>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Benefits to Stakeholders</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Borrowers: Access to legally secure, affordable home finance</li>
                <li>Lenders: Reduced risk through insurance and verified property titles</li>
                <li>Investors: Confidence in securitized instruments backed by hire-purchase agreements</li>
                <li>Government: Promotes affordable housing and financial inclusion</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Integration with FSTL Ecosystem</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Title Guarantee – ensures legal ownership and documentation</li>
                <li